- build a cli class
- welcome the user and enter user name
- prompt the user either to select a list, or to exit 

- for invalid input give the user an error message and give the user to select again
- if the user select a list, print the list of films
- and to select the film detail

- if the user select exit, print goodby message and exit from the program

- 3 classes to build
- CLI - controller - what communicate with the user and the data
- Film - where objects are created and stored for user display 
- Api - bring external data using url, consume api here, instantiate my objects 

-URL: https://gebre2020.github.io/ruby_films_cli_project/